      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA ENVY (8) is racing well without winning, recording four minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when second (29.80) over 525m at The Meadows. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature in the finish again. CUMULATE (5) could manage only second at this track last time but impressed when clocking a superb 22.55 over 400m at Geelong the start prior. Should be in this for a long way. BE A SECRET (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 3 lengths from the winner (20.04). Should be about the money. GUARDIAN (6) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
